# ─── Mediajam Production API (192.168.1.50) ───────────────────────────────────
#
# Auth:  Authorization: Bearer <API_KEY>
# Example:
#   curl -H "Authorization: Bearer $API_KEY" $BASE_URL/api/sync/status
#
# The key has full permissions: read:media, write:media, read:sync, write:sync, admin
# It does not expire.
#
# Useful endpoints:
#   GET  /api/sync/status      – current sync state
#   GET  /api/api-keys          – list registered API keys
#   GET  /api/activity          – recent activity feed
#   GET  /api/pipeline          – nightly pipeline status
#   POST /api/sync              – trigger a sync
#   GET  /api/ratings           – user ratings
#   GET  /api/conflicts         – unresolved merge conflicts
#
# NOTE: Do NOT use x-api-key header; the app expects "Authorization: Bearer mj_..."
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

